<lb n="0032b03" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0032b0301">由誦此真言，<note n="0032013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">則獲＝七遍即【甲】</note><note n="0032013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">則獲【大】，七遍即【甲】</note><app n="0032013"><lem wit="【大】">則獲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">七遍即</rdg></app>得三業清淨，則成以<note n="0032014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">功德法＝八功德【甲】</note><note n="0032014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">功德法【大】，八功德【甲】</note><app n="0032014"><lem wit="【大】">功
<lb n="0032b04" ed="T"/>德法</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">八功德</rdg></app>水灑浴身<note n="0032015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">心＝口意次【甲】</note><note n="0032015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">心【大】，口意次【甲】</note><app n="0032015"><lem wit="【大】">心</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">口意次</rdg></app>。則結觀自在菩薩<note n="0032016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">印＝心密印以【甲】</note><note n="0032016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">印【大】，心密印以【甲】</note><app n="0032016"><lem wit="【大】">印</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">心密印以</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0032b05" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0032b0501">二羽<note n="0032017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">相＝內【甲】</note><note n="0032017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">相【大】，內【甲】</note><app n="0032017"><lem wit="【大】">相</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">內</rdg></app>叉<note n="0032018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔作〕－【甲】</note><note n="0032018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">作【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0032018"><lem wit="【大】">作</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>拳，<note n="0032019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔以〕－【甲】</note><note n="0032019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0032019"><lem wit="【大】">以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>禪度出外<note n="0032020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔直〕－【甲】</note><note n="0032020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">直【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0032020"><lem wit="【大】">直</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>竪<note n="0032021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">即成誦心＝誦【甲】</note><note n="0032021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">即成誦心【大】，誦【甲】</note><app n="0032021"><lem wit="【大】">即成。
<lb n="0032b06" ed="T"/>誦心</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">誦</rdg></app>真言<note n="0032022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">七＝三【甲】</note><note n="0032022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">七【大】，三【甲】</note><app n="0032022"><lem wit="【大】">七</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">三</rdg></app>遍。真言曰：</p>
<lb n="0032b07" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT20p0032b0701"><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-DA42"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">唵</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-CFC6"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><cb:yin><cb:zi>阿</cb:zi><cb:sg><note n="0032023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔去〕－【甲】</note><note n="0032023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">去【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0032023"><lem wit="【大】">去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>引</cb:sg></cb:yin></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A646"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><cb:yin><cb:zi><note n="0032024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">嚧＝嚕【甲】</note><note n="0032024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嚧【大】，嚕【甲】</note><app n="0032024"><lem wit="【大】">嚧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">嚕</rdg></app></cb:zi><cb:sg><app type="star" corresp="#0032012"><lem wit="【大】">引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></cb:sg></cb:yin></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A64C"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">力</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-E15D"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><cb:yin><cb:zi>迦</cb:zi><cb:sg><note n="0032025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔半音〕－【甲】</note><note n="0032025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">半音【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0032025"><lem wit="【大】">半音</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></cb:sg></cb:yin></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-B065"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><cb:yin><cb:zi>婆嚩</cb:zi><cb:sg>二合<app type="star" corresp="#0032012"><lem wit="【大】">引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></cb:sg></cb:yin></cb:t></cb:tt>
<lb n="0032b08" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0032b09" ed="T"/><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A6A9"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><cb:yin><cb:zi>賀</cb:zi><cb:sg><app type="star" corresp="#0032012"><lem wit="【大】">引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></cb:sg></cb:yin></cb:t></cb:tt></p>
<lb n="0032b10" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0032b11" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0032b1101">由結<note n="0032026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此＝前【甲】</note><note n="0032026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">此【大】，前【甲】</note><app n="0032026"><lem wit="【大】">此</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">前</rdg></app>印<note n="0032027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔及〕－【甲】</note><note n="0032027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">及【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0032027"><lem wit="【大】">及</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>誦真<note n="0032028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">言＋（故）【甲】</note><note n="0032028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">言【大】，言故【甲】</note><app n="0032028"><lem wit="【大】">言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">言故</rdg></app>，即成三昧耶。又結前
<lb n="0032b12" ed="T"/>印誦真言三遍，以印左<note n="0032029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">繞三匝則成＝旋三遍即【甲】</note><note n="0032029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">繞三匝則成【大】，旋三遍即【甲】</note><app n="0032029"><lem wit="【大】">繞三匝，則成</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">旋三遍即</rdg></app>辟除一
<lb n="0032b13" ed="T"/>切諸魔障者。又結前印誦真言三遍，以印右
<lb n="0032b14" ed="T"/>轉三匝，<note n="0032030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">則＝即【甲】＊</note><note n="0032030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">則【大】＊，即【甲】＊</note><app n="0032030"><lem wit="【大】">則</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">即</rdg></app>成結界。</p>
<lb n="0032b15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0032b1501"><app type="star" corresp="#0032030"><lem wit="【大】">則</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">即</rdg></app>想身前<note n="0032031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（有）＋八【甲】</note><note n="0032031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">八【大】，有八【甲】</note><app n="0032031"><lem wit="【大】">八</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">有八</rdg></app>葉蓮華，又結前印誦真言七
<lb n="0032b16" ed="T"/>遍，以禪度向身招之。</p>
<lb n="0032b17" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0032b1701">則觀自在菩薩<note n="0032032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔并〕－【甲】</note><note n="0032032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">并【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0032032"><lem wit="【大】">并</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>蓮華部一切聖眾皆來集
<lb n="0032b18" ed="T"/><note n="0032033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">會＋（請加翳醯呬發遣改為<g ref="#CB00753"/>瑳<g ref="#CB00753"/>瑳）細註【甲】</note><note n="0032033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">會【大】，會<note place="inline">請加翳醯呬發遣改為<g ref="#CB00753"/>瑳<g ref="#CB00753"/>瑳</note>【甲】</note><app n="0032033"><lem wit="【大】">會</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">會<note place="inline">請加翳醯呬發遣改為<g ref="#CB00753"/>瑳<g ref="#CB00753"/>瑳</note></rdg></app>，則以二手捧閼伽香水器，當額奉獻誦真
<lb n="0032b19" ed="T"/>言七遍，想浴聖眾。</p>
<lb n="0032b20" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0032b2001">又結前印誦真言七遍，<note n="0032034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔則〕－【甲】</note><note n="0032034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">則【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0032034"><lem wit="【大】">則</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>成獻蓮華之座。</p>
<lb n="0032b21" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0032b2101">又結前印誦真言三遍，<app type="star" corresp="#0032030"><lem wit="【大】">則</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">即</rdg></app>成塗香供養。</p>
<lb n="0032b22" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0032b2201">又結前印誦真言三遍，<app type="star" corresp="#0032030"><lem wit="【大】">則</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">即</rdg></app>成<note n="0032035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（種種）＋華【甲】</note><note n="0032035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">華【大】，種種華【甲】</note><app n="0032035"><lem wit="【大】">華</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">種種華</rdg></app>鬘供<note n="0032036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">甲本養之次有又結前印誦真言三遍即成燒香供養十五字</note>養。</p>
<lb n="0032b23" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0032b2301">又結前印誦真言三遍，<app type="star" corresp="#0032030"><lem wit="【大】">則</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">即</rdg></app>成種種天<note n="0032037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔妙〕－【甲】</note><note n="0032037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">妙【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0032037"><lem wit="【大】">妙</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>飲
<lb n="0032b24" ed="T"/>食供養。</p>
<lb n="0032b25" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0032b2501">又結前印誦真言三遍，<app type="star" corresp="#0032030"><lem wit="【大】">則</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">即</rdg></app>成燈燭供養。</p>
<lb n="0032b26" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0032b2601">又結前印<note n="0032038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔當心〕－【甲】</note><note n="0032038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">當心【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0032038"><lem wit="【大】">當心</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>誦真言七遍，則想自身坐於
<lb n="0032b27" ed="T"/>八葉蓮華臺中，相好威光具足圓滿，等同觀
<lb n="0032b28" ed="T"/>自在菩薩。於蓮華八葉每一一葉上，各有
<lb n="0032b29" ed="T"/>一如來入定，面向觀自在菩薩。行者<note n="0032039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以如是＝如【甲】</note><note n="0032039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以如是【大】，如【甲】</note><app n="0032039"><lem wit="【大】">以如是</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">如</rdg></app>
<pb n="0032c" ed="T" xml:id="T20.1041.0032c"/>
<lb n="0032c01" ed="T"/>觀念極令分明，舉印於頂上<note n="0032040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">散＋（之）【甲】</note><note n="0032040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">散【大】，散之【甲】</note><app n="0032040"><lem wit="【大】">散</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">散之</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0032c02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0032c0201"><app type="star" corresp="#0032030"><lem wit="【大】">則</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">即</rdg></app>取念珠<note n="0032041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蟠＝盤【甲】</note><note n="0032041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蟠【大】，盤【甲】</note><app n="0032041"><lem wit="【大】">蟠</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">盤</rdg></app>於掌中，<note n="0032042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔合掌〕－【甲】</note><note n="0032042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">合掌【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0032042"><lem wit="【大】">合掌</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>當心，<note n="0032043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">誦＋（真言）【甲】</note><note n="0032043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">誦【大】，誦真言【甲】</note><app n="0032043"><lem wit="【大】">誦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">誦真言</rdg></app>加持
<lb n="0032c03" ed="T"/>念珠<note n="0032044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔真言〕－【甲】</note><note n="0032044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">真言【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0032044"><lem wit="【大】">真言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>七遍。真言曰：</p>
<lb n="0032c04" ed="T"/><p cb:type="dharani" xml:id="pT20p0032c0401"><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-DA42"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">唵</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A65D"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">尾</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A652"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><cb:yin><cb:zi>嚕</cb:zi><cb:sg>引</cb:sg></cb:yin></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A47C"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant">左</cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A5A9"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><cb:yin><cb:zi>曩</cb:zi><cb:sg>引</cb:sg></cb:yin></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A5E5"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><cb:yin><cb:zi>麼</cb:zi><cb:sg><note n="0032045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔鼻聲〕－【甲】</note><note n="0032045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鼻聲【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0032045"><lem wit="【大】">鼻聲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></cb:sg></cb:yin></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A64A"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><note n="0032046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">攞＋（二合引）細註【甲】</note><note n="0032046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">攞【大】，攞<note place="inline">二合引</note>【甲】</note><app n="0032046"><lem wit="【大】">攞</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">攞<note place="inline">二合引</note></rdg></app></cb:t></cb:tt><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-B065"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><cb:yin><cb:zi>娑<note n="0032047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">嚩＝婆【甲】</note><note n="0032047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嚩【大】，婆【甲】</note><app n="0032047"><lem wit="【大】">嚩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">婆</rdg></app></cb:zi><cb:sg>二合<app type="star" corresp="#0032012"><lem wit="【大】">引</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></cb:sg></cb:yin></cb:t></cb:tt>
<lb n="0032c05" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0032c06" ed="T"/><cb:tt><cb:t xml:lang="sa-Sidd"><g ref="#SD-A6A9"/></cb:t><cb:t xml:lang="zh-Hant"><cb:yin><cb:zi>賀</cb:zi><cb:sg>引</cb:sg></cb:yin></cb:t></cb:tt></p>
<lb n="0032c07" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0032c08" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0032c0801">則二手當心，各聚五指如未敷蓮華形，當心
<lb n="0032c09" ed="T"/><note n="0032048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">誦＋（心）【甲】</note><note n="0032048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">誦【大】，誦心【甲】</note><app n="0032048"><lem wit="【大】">誦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">誦心</rdg></app>真言，不緩不急<note n="0032049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">歷＋（然）【甲】</note><note n="0032049" resp="CBETA" type="mod">歷【大】，歷然【甲】</note><app n="0032049"><lem wit="【大】">歷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">歷然</rdg></app>分明不應出聲。寂靜
<lb n="0032c10" ed="T"/>念誦，每<note n="0032050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">與＝待【甲】</note><note n="0032050" resp="CBETA" type="mod">與【大】，待【甲】</note><app n="0032050"><lem wit="【大】">與</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">待</rdg></app>真言後字聲<note n="0032051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（絕）＋齊【甲】</note><note n="0032051" resp="CBETA" type="mod">齊【大】，絕齊【甲】</note><app n="0032051"><lem wit="【大】">齊</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">絕齊</rdg></app>移一珠，於<note n="0032052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔心〕－【甲】</note><note n="0032052" resp="CBETA" type="mod">心【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0032052"><lem wit="【大】">心</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>真
<lb n="0032c11" ed="T"/>言句中去初後字。念誦之時勿令散亂，身心
<lb n="0032c12" ed="T"/>凝寂更不異緣，唯觀本尊專注念誦。<note n="0032053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">則觀＝即【甲】</note><note n="0032053" resp="CBETA" type="mod">則觀【大】，即【甲】</note><app n="0032053"><lem wit="【大】">則觀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">即</rdg></app>
<lb n="0032c13" ed="T"/>想身前八葉蓮華上，有觀自在菩薩相好圓
<lb n="0032c14" ed="T"/>滿處月輪中，復觀自身同彼觀自在菩薩等
<lb n="0032c15" ed="T"/>無<note n="0032054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">差別＝有異【甲】</note><note n="0032054" resp="CBETA" type="mod">差別【大】，有異【甲】</note><app n="0032054"><lem wit="【大】">差別</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">有異</rdg></app>。念誦數畢，捧珠頂戴，起慈悲心發大
<lb n="0032c16" ed="T"/>誓<note n="0032055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">願＋（願）【甲】</note><note n="0032055" resp="CBETA" type="mod">願【大】，願願【甲】</note><app n="0032055"><lem wit="【大】">願</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">願願</rdg></app>：「一切有情所希<note n="0032056" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">望＋（願世出）【甲】</note><note n="0032056" resp="CBETA" type="mod">望【大】，望願世出【甲】</note><app n="0032056"><lem wit="【大】">望</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">望願世出</rdg></app>世間殊勝上願，速
<lb n="0032c17" ed="T"/>得成就。」則安珠<note n="0032057" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（於）＋本【甲】</note><note n="0032057" resp="CBETA" type="mod">本【大】，於本【甲】</note><app n="0032057"><lem wit="【大】">本</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">於本</rdg></app>處。</p>
<lb n="0032c18" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0032c1801"><note n="0032058" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">又＝則【甲】</note><note n="0032058" resp="CBETA" type="mod">又【大】，則【甲】</note><app n="0032058"><lem wit="【大】">又</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">則</rdg></app>結前印當心，誦真言七遍，即成三昧<note n="0032059" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">耶＋（護身印）【甲】</note><note n="0032059" resp="CBETA" type="mod">耶【大】，耶護身印【甲】</note><app n="0032059"><lem wit="【大】">耶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">耶護身印</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0032c19" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0032c1901">復以<note n="0032060" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（其）＋印【甲】</note><note n="0032060" resp="CBETA" type="mod">印【大】，其印【甲】</note><app n="0032060"><lem wit="【大】">印</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">其印</rdg></app>加持自身五處，所謂額<note n="0032061" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">上右肩左＝左肩右【甲】</note><note n="0032061" resp="CBETA" type="mod">上右肩左【大】，左肩右【甲】</note><app n="0032061"><lem wit="【大】">上、右肩、左</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">左肩右</rdg></app>
<lb n="0032c20" ed="T"/>肩、心上及喉，是名五處，<note n="0032062" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">各＋（隨印處）【甲】</note><note n="0032062" resp="CBETA" type="mod">各【大】，各隨印處【甲】</note><app n="0032062"><lem wit="【大】">各</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">各隨印處</rdg></app>誦真言一遍加
<lb n="0032c21" ed="T"/><note n="0032063" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">持＋（已）【甲】</note><note n="0032063" resp="CBETA" type="mod">持【大】，持已【甲】</note><app n="0032063"><lem wit="【大】">持</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">持已</rdg></app>，頂上散印。</p>
<lb n="0032c22" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0032c2201">又結前印如<note n="0032064" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">前＋（印奉）【甲】</note><note n="0032064" resp="CBETA" type="mod">前【大】，前印奉【甲】</note><app n="0032064"><lem wit="【大】">前</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">前印奉</rdg></app>，獻五種供養，各誦真言一遍，
<pb n="0033a" ed="T" xml:id="T20.1041.0033a"/>
<lb n="0033a01" ed="T"/><app type="star" corresp="#0032030"><lem wit="【大】">則</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">即</rdg></app>成廣<note n="0033001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">大＋（殊勝）【甲】</note><note n="0033001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">大【大】，大殊勝【甲】</note><app n="0033001"><lem wit="【大】">大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">大殊勝</rdg></app>供養。則以二手捧閼伽<note n="0033002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（香）＋水【甲】</note><note n="0033002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">水【大】，香水【甲】</note><app n="0033002"><lem wit="【大】">水</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">香水</rdg></app>，當額
<lb n="0033a02" ed="T"/>奉獻，誦真言一遍。</p>
<lb n="0033a03" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0033a0301">又結前印左轉一匝，<app type="star" corresp="#0032030"><lem wit="【大】">則</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">即</rdg></app>成解界。</p>
<lb n="0033a04" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0033a0401">又結前印，以禪度向外擲之，誦真言三遍，舉
<lb n="0033a05" ed="T"/>印安<note n="0033003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">頂＝於頂上【甲】</note><note n="0033003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">頂【大】，於頂上【甲】</note><app n="0033003"><lem wit="【大】">頂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">於頂上</rdg></app>，<app type="star" corresp="#0032030"><lem wit="【大】">則</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">即</rdg></app>成奉送一切聖眾。</p>
<lb n="0033a06" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0033a0601">又結前<note n="0033004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">印＋（如前）【甲】</note><note n="0033004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">印【大】，印如前【甲】</note><app n="0033004"><lem wit="【大】">印</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">印如前</rdg></app>加持自身五處，<note n="0033005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔各誦真言一遍〕－【甲】</note><note n="0033005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">各誦真言一遍【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0033005"><lem wit="【大】">各誦真言一遍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，
<lb n="0033a07" ed="T"/>則成被甲，頂上散<note n="0033006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">印＝之【甲】</note><note n="0033006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">印【大】，之【甲】</note><app n="0033006"><lem wit="【大】">印</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">之</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0033a08" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0033a0801">修行者如是<note n="0033007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔依此〕－【甲】</note><note n="0033007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">依此【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0033007"><lem wit="【大】">依此</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>祕密法要，精誠<note n="0033008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔念誦〕－【甲】</note><note n="0033008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">念誦【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0033008"><lem wit="【大】">念誦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>作
<lb n="0033a09" ed="T"/>意修持，一切所為速得成就，世出世間諸願
<lb n="0033a10" ed="T"/>圓滿，業障消<note n="0033009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">除＝滅【甲】</note><note n="0033009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">除【大】，滅【甲】</note><app n="0033009"><lem wit="【大】">除</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">滅</rdg></app>，三昧現前，不轉此身騰空自
<lb n="0033a11" ed="T"/>在隨意，即往十方淨土歷事諸佛，速成無上
<lb n="0033a12" ed="T"/>菩提。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0033a13" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead><note n="0033010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（聖）＋觀【甲】</note><note n="0033010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">觀【大】，聖觀【甲】</note><app n="0033010"><lem wit="【大】">觀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">聖觀</rdg></app>自在菩薩<note n="0033011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔心真言〕－【甲】</note><note n="0033011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">心真言【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0033011"><lem wit="【大】">心真言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>一印念誦法</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0033a14" ed="T"/><note n="0033012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔八家…也〕四十三字－【甲】</note><note n="0033012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（八家…也）四十三字【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0033012" cb:word-count="43"><lem wit="【大】"><cb:div type="w"><p xml:id="pT20p0033a1401">八家祕錄云：</p>
<lb n="0033a15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0033a1501">觀自在菩薩心真言一印念誦法<note place="inline">仁</note>不空</p>
<lb n="0033a16" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT20p0033a1601">此中仁者圓仁，即慈覺大師之諱也。此本
<lb n="0033a17" ed="T"/>則慈覺請來也。</p></cb:div></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
</body></text></TEI>